==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Photovisual
<hw>Pho`to*vis"u*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Optics)</fld>
<def>Of certain achromatic lenses, having the same focus for the actinic
and for the brightest of the visual rays.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Photoxylography</ent>⟦br⟧
